body:
1. registered javascript witch starts with every page
<br>2. api to add button from this script near address bar
<br>3. api to add menu item into menu
<br>example of plugin file:
<br>&lt;plugin&gt; 
<br>	&lt;title&gt;Forward button plugin&lt;/title&gt;
<br>    &lt;description&gt;Forward button plugin&lt;/description&gt;
<br>	&lt;button&gt;
<br>		&lt;icon&gt;base64_encoded_icon&lt;/icon&gt;
<br>		&lt;script&gt;&lt;![CDATA[ 
<br>		history.forward();
<br>		]]&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
<br>	&lt;/button&gt;
<br>	&lt;menuItems&gt;
<br>		&lt;menuItem title="Forward" position="0"&gt;
<br>		&lt;script&gt;&lt;![CDATA[ 
<br>		history.forward();
<br>		]]&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
<br>		&lt;/menuItem&gt;
<br>	&lt;/menuItems&gt;
<br>	&lt;events&gt;
<br>		&lt;event name="onload"&gt;
<br>		&lt;script&gt;&lt;![CDATA[ 
<br>		document.write("Plugin loaded");
<br>		]]&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
<br>		&lt;/event&gt;
<br>	&lt;/events&gt;	
<br>&lt;/plugin&gt;
